        BoomSpikeSlab, tseries, urca, vars, progressr, future.apply,
        rlang, magrittr, parallel, stats, utils
Suggests: knitr, cmdstanr, rstan, future, RhpcBLASctl, rmarkdown,
        testthat (>= 3.0.0)
